      "correct_choice_id": 0,
      "solution": "<p><strong>Correct Answer: A) A alpha</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>Explanation: </strong>The nerve fibers responsible for the transmission of <strong>proprioception</strong> are<strong> A <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"a9268f2e1d16927771814cfef69cf4\">alpha</span> fibers </strong></p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:780px\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"8\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:1px solid black\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Classification of nerve fibres - Erlanger and Gasser and Lloyd-Hunt </strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Fiber Type</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Erlanger-Gasser Classification</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Lloyd-Hunt Classification</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Myelination</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Function</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Conduction Velocity (m/s)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Diameter (µm)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><strong>Sensitivity to Blockade</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aα</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aα</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Ia, Ib</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"5\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Myelinated</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Proprioception, <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"3db910d8571692777198303e3bcb27\">somatic</span> motor</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>70-120</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>12-20</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Pressure - Most susceptible</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aβ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aβ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>II</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Touch, pressure</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>(Option B)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>30-70</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>5-12</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"3\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Pressure - Intermediate.</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aγ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aγ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Motor to muscle spindles</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>(Option C)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>15-30</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>3-6</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aδ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Aδ</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>III</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Pain (fast), temperature (cold)</p>\n\n\t\t\t<p><strong>(Option D)</strong></p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>12-30</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>2-5</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>B</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>B</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Preganglionic autonomic</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>3-15</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p><3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Hypoxia - Most susceptible</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>C<br />\n\t\t\t(Dorsal Root)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>C</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>IV</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Unmyelinated</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Pain (slow), temperature (warm)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>0.5-2</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>0.4-1.2</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td rowspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Local anesthetics - Most susceptible</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>C (Sympathetic)</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>C</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p> </p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>Postganglionic sympathetic</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>0.7-2.3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; border-left:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-top:none\">\n\t\t\t<p>0.3-1.3</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>",
