      "solution": "<p>Tactile discrimination, which refers to the ability to discern fine details, textures, and shapes through touch, relies on <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ebb480187d1692777199e233e9e356\">superficial</span> <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"408bcde7f01692777198acadb8e1c6\">sensory</span> receptors in the skin.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>Both Merkel discs and Meissner’s corpuscles are involved in <span class=\"customMeta\" data-dictid=\"ff110f2cb71692777200a3483aa670\">tactile</span> discrimination, allowing individuals to sense and distinguish intricate textures and shapes.</p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>Specialized mechanoreceptors</strong></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:NaN\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\"><img alt=\"Meissners \" data-author=\"NA\" data-hash=\"12619\" data-license=\"NA\" data-source=\"NA\" data-tags=\"May2025\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/notes/wk6x8P5Oi0y1CAGJwvOW1747059492.png\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\"><img alt=\"Merkel \" data-author=\"NA\" data-hash=\"12622\" data-license=\"NA\" data-source=\"NA\" data-tags=\"May2025\" src=\"https://image.prepladder.com/notes/4GWv0l5cuLXt3NsdE2EJ1747059710.png\" />\n\t\t\t<figcaption>{{caption_text}}</figcaption>\n\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid #000000; border-left:1px solid #000000; border-right:1px solid #000000; border-top:1px solid #000000; vertical-align:top\">\n\t\t\t<figure class=\"caption_element\"><img alt=\"Pacini